<file path="README.md">
# RAG Internal Knowledge

Hệ thống RAG (Retrieval-Augmented Generation) cho thông tin nội bộ. Upload tài liệu (PDF, DOCX, TXT, MD), tự động xử lý & lưu trữ vector embeddings, trả lời câu hỏi dựa trên nội dung tài liệu. Hoàn toàn self-hosted, không phụ thuộc API bên ngoài.

## Tech Stack

| Component | Technology |
|-----------|-----------|
| Backend | Python 3.11, FastAPI, SQLAlchemy 2.0 |
| Vector DB | PostgreSQL 16 + pgvector |
| Embeddings | sentence-transformers (all-MiniLM-L6-v2, 384 dims) |
| LLM | Ollama + Qwen3 8B (self-hosted, thay đổi được) |
| Frontend | React 18, TypeScript, Vite, Tailwind CSS |
| Auth | JWT (24h expiry, bcrypt) |
| Container | Docker + Docker Compose |

## Quick Start

### Docker (recommended)

```bash
# 1. Clone & configure
cp backend/.env.example backend/.env
# Edit backend/.env: set SECRET_KEY

# 2. Start all services (includes Ollama)
docker compose up -d

# 3. Pull LLM model (first time only, ~5GB)
docker compose exec ollama ollama pull qwen3:8b

# 4. Access
# Frontend: http://localhost:3000
# Backend API: http://localhost:8000
# API Docs: http://localhost:8000/docs
```

### Local Development

**Backend:**
```bash
cd backend
cp .env.example .env
# Edit .env: set SECRET_KEY, OLLAMA_BASE_URL

poetry install
poetry run alembic upgrade head
poetry run uvicorn src.main:app --reload
```

**Frontend:**
```bash
cd frontend
npm install
npm run dev
# Access: http://localhost:5173
```

**Prerequisites:**
- Python 3.11+
- Node.js 20+
- PostgreSQL 16 with pgvector extension
- Ollama (https://ollama.com) with a pulled model

## Architecture

```
[React Frontend]  -->  [FastAPI Backend]
                           |
                  [Document Pipeline]
                  - Upload & parse (PDF/DOCX/TXT/MD)
                  - Chunk (512 tokens, 50 overlap)
                  - Embed (sentence-transformers)
                  - Store (pgvector)
                           |
                  [RAG Engine]
                  - Query embedding
                  - Vector similarity search (cosine)
                  - Context assembly
                  - Ollama LLM generation (streaming)
                           |
                  [PostgreSQL + pgvector]
```

## API Endpoints

| Method | Path | Description |
|--------|------|-------------|
| POST | /auth/register | Register new user |
| POST | /auth/login | Login, get JWT token |
| POST | /documents/upload | Upload document (multipart) |
| GET | /documents | List user's documents |
| GET | /documents/{id} | Document detail |
| DELETE | /documents/{id} | Delete document |
| POST | /rag/query | Query RAG (full response) |
| POST | /rag/query-stream | Query RAG (SSE streaming) |
| GET | /health | Health check |

## Project Structure

```
.
├── docker-compose.yml
├── backend/
│   ├── src/
│   │   ├── main.py              # FastAPI app
│   │   ├── config.py            # Settings
│   │   ├── auth/                # Authentication (JWT)
│   │   ├── documents/           # Document upload & processing
│   │   ├── rag/                 # RAG query engine
│   │   ├── embeddings/          # Embedding service
│   │   └── db/                  # Database layer
│   ├── alembic/                 # DB migrations
│   └── tests/
└── frontend/
    └── src/
        ├── api/                 # API client layer
        ├── components/          # Reusable UI components
        ├── pages/               # Route pages
        ├── hooks/               # Custom React hooks
        └── contexts/            # Auth context
```
